{"tid":1578791,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"坪石邨女子墮樓亡","createTime":"2019-09-18T09:25:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T10:04:13.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f775e3295393d5913fea759325e9cd9934e67498","tid":1578791,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:25:55.000Z","msg":"牛池灣有人墮樓。今早(18日)10時54分，一名中年婦由坪石邨黃石樓高處墮下，倒臥地上重傷昏迷，姓郭(28歲)男途人行經發現，慌忙報警求助。救護員接報趕至，將墮樓女子送往聯合醫院搶救，惜送院後終告不治，現場遺下一攤血漬。<br />\n<br />\n警方封鎖現場，惟未有檢獲遺書，經初步調查後，證實墮樓婦姓何(61歲)，生前疑有身體病紀錄，不排除因而輕生，相信她由上址一房間墮下，事件沒有可疑，惟何的死因有待驗屍確定。 <br />\n<br />\n 防止自殺求助熱線：<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222<br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000<br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288<br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000<br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281<br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350<br />\n利民會： 3512 2626<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」： <a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=Ii72mHdDrz30Fn2z87Evj6ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=8b6f3311\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.openup.hk</a> <br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190918/bkn-20190918110628740-0918_00822_001.html</code></pre>"},{"pid":"5b624fd9975c9737481577c1dcc0cd40ba51942e","tid":1578791,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:26:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球響應「929全球集會抗赤納粹」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全世界一齊對準極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577380</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWqVmOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWqVmOV.jpg&h=075c7745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1tov9s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1tov9s.png&h=0af09f95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"55fa8187526d38d0ad9ca5d08b2fd27cf2424751","tid":1578791,"uid":31200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:27:41.000Z","msg":"又多一件冇可疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"729215830ceffb57e3fc64659bbaf4f3fcba5d23","tid":1578791,"uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:28:08.000Z","msg":"家屬rip"},{"pid":"b815c56c4ff893585fa18e57558e190b0c6cd156","tid":1578791,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:28:22.000Z","msg":"【9.23~9.27】全球「反共」聯軍來了我帶路！快閃式萬國「民主」旗號召世界<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eccnjS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eccnjS</a><br />\n<blockquote><br />\n由於香港身為<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>東道主</strong></span></span>倘若因為任何原因而令到遊行人數小得難睇, 是不理想的！<br />\n<br />\n同埋我寧願<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>10.1國殤</strong></span>打到拆天就最好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當然大家請記著呢日唔是End-game<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 由美帝反共眾議員可以見到場戰爭並非一朝一夕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 失去所有勇武運動將難以持續<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家講到星期日9.29是全球性<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 單靠香港人文宣團隊twitter retweet比當地人是難以收到巨大宣傳效益<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">唯有無比juicy<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />方法去呼喚他國人民, 同埋件事夠juicy<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />外國媒體先會幫你免費頭版</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong>【9.23~9.27】全球「反共」聯軍來了我帶路！<br />\n集合時間：1930~2000<br />\n遊行時間：2000~終點和平散去 (預計9點前行到遮打即龍頭散去)<br />\n舉行日期：9月23日至9月27日晚上快閃式遊行<br />\n遊行路線：修頓球場 至 遮打花園<br />\n注意事項：遊行完就即時由中環遮打盡快散去！不起衝突！人小就行行人路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n衣著：遊行時黑色, 前往及離開時非黑色<br />\n快閃遊行目的：號召全球「反共」聯軍同時響應9.29大遊行, 盡可能與香港同步舉行！</strong></span><br />\n利申：是次遊行屬自發性質, 沒有不反對通知書<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講到反共你走去申請唔好傻啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我主張每晚均可見到頭60名民主國度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只要有60位手足舉60支旗個畫面已經夠晒Juicy<br />\n首先你話該國家一直龜縮有咩撚用,舉嚟把撚啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但是9.29反共大遊行號召目標是各國人民,<br />\n如果我地真是連續一星期舉民主國家國旗, <span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>當地右翼會相當自豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>,<br />\n同埋每晚我地可以twitter開放檢討比各國人民知道其國旗在香港揚起以打倒中共</blockquote>"},{"pid":"861287bd86749aab3eee23c9a628e762096eacb5","tid":1578791,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:28:56.000Z","msg":"呀~~"},{"pid":"61cd71efc5793bb3d633f79417211916b8249961","tid":1578791,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:29:22.000Z","msg":"831 rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee9670afe7706a78c3ddb56864f64cccc1c94b95","tid":1578791,"uid":266172,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:29:35.000Z","msg":"832同918差好遠，法醫驗屍會確認到死去日期，唔洗太陰謀論。只不過為死者家屬同死者送上一分鐘沉默都係需要的。<br />\n希望佢家人可以睇開d。"},{"pid":"e7b95a0e5ec2a626515c9644f17aab9ff84141de","tid":1578791,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ee9670afe7706a78c3ddb56864f64cccc1c94b95","tid":1578791,"uid":266172,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:29:35.000Z","msg":"832同918差好遠，法醫驗屍會確認到死去日期，唔洗太陰謀論。只不過為死者家屬同死者送上一分鐘沉默都係需要的。<br />\n希望佢家人可以睇開d。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime